{"_path":"/maps/_ai/agents","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"智能体 (AI Agents)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"智能体-ai-agents"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智能体 (AI Agents)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"langchain构建-llm-应用的编排框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain：构建 LLM 应用的编排框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 提供构建 LLM 应用的标准组件：Chains（将多个 LLM 调用串联成工作流）、Agents（动态决策调用哪些工具）、Memory（对话历史管理）、Callbacks（日志、监控集成）。支持 ReAct（推理+行动交替）、Plan-and-Execute（先制定计划再执行）、Structured Chat（结构化输出解析）等 Agent 类型。是构建复杂 LLM 应用的首选框架。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://langchain.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.langchain.com/react-agent-benchmarking/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ReAct Agent 基准测试"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gi7nqB37WEY","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain Agents 教程"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llamaindex数据增强的-agent-开发框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex：数据增强的 Agent 开发框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex 专注于\"数据增强的 Agent\"——连接 LLM 与私有数据。提供 100+ Data Connectors（PDF、SQL、API 等数据源）、多种 Index Types（向量索引、树索引、图索引）、Query Engines（RAG、多文档问答）。Workflow 机制允许定义复杂的 Agent 协作流程，结合工具调用与检索能力，是 RAG 和知识库应用的首选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.llamaindex.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/framework/understanding/rag/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex RAG 指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.llamaindex.ai/blog/automate-workflows-with-document-agents-a-complete-tutorial-to-building-context-aware-AI","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Document Agents 工作流"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"crewai多-agent-协作框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI：多 Agent 协作框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 将 Agent 定义为具有角色、目标和工具的\"数字员工\"，通过定义任务依赖实现协作。支持 Role-Playing Agents（专业化角色设定）、Autonomous Collaboration（自主协作）、Task Delegation（任务委托）。适合研究报告生成、代码审查流水线、客户服务自动化等需要多角色协作的场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.crewai.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.crewai.com/en/introduction","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/crewai-crash-course-role-based-agent-orchestration","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 实战指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"autogpt自主-agent-先驱"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT：自主 Agent 先驱"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT 是首个引发广泛关注的自主 Agent 项目，展示了 LLM 独立完成任务的可能性：目标分解将大目标拆分为可执行步骤、自主循环（观察-思考-行动-记忆）、工具使用（文件操作、网络搜索、代码执行）。但也面临循环陷阱、成本失控、可靠性等现实挑战，更多用于探索性任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/Significant-Gravitas/AutoGPT","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"框架选择指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"框架选择指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 适合复杂 LLM 应用，学习曲线中等；LlamaIndex 适合 RAG 和知识库，学习曲线平缓；CrewAI 适合多角色协作场景，学习曲线平缓；AutoGPT 适合探索性任务，学习曲线陡峭。实际项目中常组合使用，如 LlamaIndex 负责数据检索，LangChain 负责工具编排，CrewAI 负责多 Agent 协作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://damodev.csdn.net/69671cabea53844658f6afed.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 主流 AI Agent 框架调研"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://draftnrun.com/en/blog/250915-ai-agent-frameworks-comparison/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain vs LlamaIndex vs CrewAI 对比"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"langchain构建-llm-应用的编排框架","depth":2,"text":"LangChain：构建 LLM 应用的编排框架"},{"id":"llamaindex数据增强的-agent-开发框架","depth":2,"text":"LlamaIndex：数据增强的 Agent 开发框架"},{"id":"crewai多-agent-协作框架","depth":2,"text":"CrewAI：多 Agent 协作框架"},{"id":"autogpt自主-agent-先驱","depth":2,"text":"AutoGPT：自主 Agent 先驱"},{"id":"框架选择指南","depth":2,"text":"框架选择指南"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:agents.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/agents.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/agents","_extension":"md"}